latestIgtvVideos.title: Fall off -remix
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A new remix to one of the hardest songs from @realkrsna new album, 
'Still here'. Just so we are clear, I did not produce the first beat. I have taken it from the original song. However, the second beat, is authentic, even though the melody used is just a variation of the main original beat.
WHATEVER. 
#falloffremixchallenge
The point is I made the second beat, inspired from the first one.
Hope you enjoy it.
